  15,55,They dictus bonus news nos dedit vos est true perfecit non despair
  15,56,He dictus Nullus despairs his Dominus mercy absque strayers
  15,57,He dictus Quod est tuus mission O messengers
  15,58,They dictus Nos dispatched guilty people
  15,59,Prout pro Lot's familia nos save them totus
